'''喬恩·「雷洪」·菲利普斯'''（英語：Jon "rejon" Phillips ，{{bd|1979年|5月28日}}），是一名開放原始碼開發者、藝術家、設計師、作家、教育工作者、專業講員和藝術館長，擁有超過12年在電腦文化中創立社群和工作經驗。他創立並發展Fabricatorz LLC，從2008年開始營運，服務包括[[Google|Google]]、[[Mozilla|Mozilla]] 和[[創用CC|創用CC]]（Creative Commons）等客戶。他目前是[[社會網路|社會網路]]公司[[Status.Net|Status.Net]]的社群主管。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://status.net/2009/10/22/jon-phillips-rejon-joins-statusnet |title=Jon Phillips (rejon) Joins StatusNet |accessdate=2015-01-10 |archive-date=2014-02-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140226021050/http://status.net/2009/10/22/jon-phillips-rejon-joins-statusnet/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.barrythrew.com/2010/10/21/status-net-at-blog-world-expo/ |title=Status.net at Blog World Expo |access-date=2015-01-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402110749/http://www.barrythrew.com/2010/10/21/status-net-at-blog-world-expo/ |archive-date=2015-04-02 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

== 生平和工作 ==

2002年，他協助發行開放原始碼繪圖工具[[Inkscape|Inkscape]]。2004年，他建立開放美工圖庫（[[Openclipart|Openclipart]]），並共同建立[[開放字型庫|開放字型庫]]（[[Open_Font_Library|Open Font Library]]）。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://fossasia.org/speakers/jon-phillips |title=http://fossasia.org/speakers/jon-phillips |accessdate=2015-01-10 |archive-date=2014-02-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140201205823/http://fossasia.org/speakers/jon-phillips |dead-url=yes }}</ref>他與[[巴塞爾．薩法迪|巴塞爾．薩法迪]]（Bassel Safadi）一起建立了[[Aiki架構|Aiki架構]]（Aiki Framework）來執行[[OCAL|OCAL]]和[[OFLB|OFLB]]，並共同創辦了Arki Lab公司，專門從事Aiki架構上層的建造。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://fabricatorz.com/2011/09/fabricatorz-and-aiki-lab-to-facilitate-open-source-developers-workshop-in-collaboration-with-ictqatar-and-creative-commons-qatar/ |title=Fabricatorz and Aiki Lab to Facilitate Open Source Developers Workshop in Collaboration With ictQATAR and Creative Commons Qatar |accessdate=2015-01-10 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304191605/http://fabricatorz.com/2011/09/fabricatorz-and-aiki-lab-to-facilitate-open-source-developers-workshop-in-collaboration-with-ictqatar-and-creative-commons-qatar/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://mastersofmedia.hum.uva.nl/2010/07/12/bringing-the-libre-an-interview-with-free-software-developer-jon-phillips/ |title=Bringing the Libre: An Interview with Free Software Developer Jon Phillips |accessdate=2015-01-10 |archive-date=2016-04-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160401045948/http://mastersofmedia.hum.uva.nl/2010/07/12/bringing-the-libre-an-interview-with-free-software-developer-jon-phillips/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>他曾在舊金山藝術學院（[[San_Francisco_Art_Institute|San Francisco Art Institute]]）教授設計和科技。他也是[[Qi_hardware|Qi hardware]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://musicworld3d.mi2n.com/press.php3?press_nb=142018 |title=Milkymist One Video Synthesizer Shown At 6th Libre Graphics Meeting In Montreal |accessdate=2015-01-10 |archive-date=2018-03-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180326203244/http://musicworld3d.mi2n.com/press.php3?press_nb=142018 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>（[[copyleft硬體|copyleft硬體]]）的共同創辦人，研發生產Milkymist One視訊合成器（[[Video_synthesizer|Video synthesizer]]）<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://lekernel.net/blog/2011/07/jon-phillips-presents-the-milkymist-one-at-fisl-12-in-porto-alegre/ |title=Jon Phillips presents the Milkymist One at FISL 12 in Porto Alegre |accessdate=2015-01-10 |archive-date=2011-07-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110723181529/http://lekernel.net/blog/2011/07/jon-phillips-presents-the-milkymist-one-at-fisl-12-in-porto-alegre/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。他和[[毛向輝|毛向輝]]（Isaac Mao）、[[克里斯多福．亞當斯|克里斯多福．亞當斯]]（Christopher Adams）一起領導[[分享主義計劃|分享主義計劃]]（Sharism project）。

